INSERT INTO `newss` VALUES (3,'VIETTEL POST CHUYN PHT NHANH HNG HA C  VIT','internal_news','2023-05-23 07:28:43.080000','2023-08-14 02:38:12.370000','2023-05-25 10:46:57.147000',2,1,'vi-VN',1,'Nhn thy tim nng th trng cng nh th mnh trong lnh vc Logistics, thng 06/2023, Viettel Post  gia nhp vo mng li chuyn pht nhanh tuyn c- Vit vi cc dch v bao gm: Chuyn hng thng mi in t h cho khch hng; Chuyn hng t c v Vit Nam cho khch hng c nhn v doanh nghip; Dch v lm th tc thng quan, nhp khu.\n\n','Viettel-post-chuyen-phat-nhanh-hang-hoa-uc-viet',281,14,11,'<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">Tim nng t i tc thng mi ln th 7 ca Vit Nam</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Thng tin ny c a ra ti cuc hp ln th 4 Nhm cng tc v Thng mi thuc khun kh Hi ngh B trng i tc kinh t Vit Nam  c c t chc vo cui thng 03/2023. Theo , trong nm 2022, kt qu thng mi hai chiu gia Vit Nam v c tng trng n tng, kim ngch song phng nm 2022 t 15,7 t USD (Ngun: Cng thng tin in t B Cng thng).</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Cng vi , hng ng k nim 50 nm Quan h Ngoi giao Vit Nam  c,  thc y hn na quan h thng mi song phng, tng xng vi quan h i tc chin lc ng thi a quan h thng mi theo hng cn bng, bn vng, Vit Nam v c nht tr thc y trin khai mt s ni dung hp tc quan trng, trong  c hp tc, chia s kinh nghim v xc tin thng mi v chui cung ng (Logistics).</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Theo Statista (Cng thng tin d liu kinh t s ton cu), hin nay, c nm trong TOP 10 quc gia c doanh thu chuyn pht, chuyn pht nhanh bu kin ton cu (CEP) ln nht th gii vi khong 12,2 t USD v d kin tng trng kp (CARG) tng 5,46% trong giai on 2022-2027.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Ti Vit Nam, doanh thu CEP c tnh t 0,71 t USD vo nm 2021 v d kin t 4,48 t USD vo nm 2030 vi CARG t 24,1%. Lng hng ha CEP t c v Vit Nam c tnh trung bnh t 200 tn/thng v cng hng khng Ni Bi v Tn Sn Nht.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Bn cnh , vi khong 335 ngn ngi Vit Nam ang sinh sng, hc tp, lm vic ti c, hot ng thng mi v logistics c  Vit c nhn nh l mt th trng nhiu trin vng.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">Viettel Post gia nhp mng li chuyn pht nhanh c  Vit</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Nhn thy tim nng th trng cng nh th mnh trong lnh vc Logistics, thng 06/2023, Viettel Post  gia nhp vo mng li chuyn pht nhanh tuyn c- Vit vi cc dch v bao gm: Chuyn hng thng mi in t h cho khch hng; Chuyn hng t c v Vit Nam cho khch hng c nhn v doanh nghip; Dch v lm th tc thng quan, nhp khu.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Vi mng li bu cc 63 tnh thnh trn c nc, dch v chuyn pht nhanh hng ha c  Vit ca Viettel Post to c s khc bit khi cung cp dch v giao hng nhanh tn nh (D2D) m khng cn thng qua bn th ba. iu ny gip rt ngn qu trnh vn chuyn khi hng ha n tay khch hng ch mt t 5 ngy lm vic.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Tnh n thng 06/2023, Viettel Post l mt trong nhng doanh nghip chuyn pht hng u ti Vit Nam, s hu mng li hn 4.000 im chuyn pht tip nhn hng ho trn ton quc, gn 40.000 CBNV chuyn nghip, 2.000 xe ti cc loi hot ng 24/24; vi t l giao thnh cng lun t mc 95%.<meta cha