nt:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Thc hin ch o ca Chnh ph, Th tng Chnh ph, cc th tc lin quan ti hot ng xut-nhp khu hng ha thi gian qua lin tc c ci cch, to thun li cho doanh nghip v nng cao nng lc cnh tranh quc gia.</span></i></span></h2><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Kt qu kho st mi c Lin on Thng mi v Cng nghip Vit Nam (VCCI) cng b cho thy, s ng doanh nghip t ra hi lng vi C ch mt ca quc gia v ci cch trong kim tra chuyn ngnh, to thun li cho hng ha xut-nhp khu. Thng k kt qu xut-nhp khu hng ha trn thc t cng cho thy iu </span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Du hiu tch cc t xut-nhp khu hng ha</strong></span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">T u nm ti nay, nhng h ly do dch Covid-19 gy ra cho nn kinh t ton cu cc k nng n. Thm vo , xung t v kinh t, qun s gia cc quc gia trn th gii cng khin nhng kh khn cho kinh t th gii thm trm trng. Gi c nhin-vt liu tng cao, cc chui cung ng, tiu th hng ha b t gy trn ton cu y gi c hng ha v lm pht tng vt, sn xut, kinh doanh b nh n, phc hi rt yu t  khp ni trn th gii. iu   nh hng rt ln ti tnh hnh sn xut, kinh doanh ca cc doanh nghip Vit Nam.</span></span></p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\" src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/image_0ea6e7fa20.png\" alt=\"image.png\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_image_0ea6e7fa20.png 232w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_image_0ea6e7fa20.png 500w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/medium_image_0ea6e7fa20.png 750w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"750\" height=\"405\" uploadprocessed=\"true\"></figure><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:center;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ngnh hi quan tng cng ng dng cng ngh thng tin, s ha trong quy trnh qun l, thc hin ngnh hi quan.</span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">S liu t&nbsp;</span></span><a style=\"text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.qdnd.vn/tag/tong-cuc-thong-ke-1017.html\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#1155cc;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><u>Tng cc Thng k&nbsp;</u></span></span></a><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">cho thy, tng kim ngch xut-nhp khu hng ha nm 2021 ca Vit Nam t 668,5 t USD, tng 22,6% so vi nm 2020. Cn theo s liu t Tng cc Hi quan, trong thng 10-2022, tng tr gi xut-nhp khu hng ha ca Vit Nam c t 58,27 t USD, tng 70 triu USD so vi thng trc. Trong , tng tr gi xut khu c t 30,27 t USD, tng 1,5% (tng ng tng 452 triu USD) v tng tr gi nhp khu c t 28 t USD, gim 1,3% (tng ng gim 382 triu USD). Tng tr gi xut-nhp khu ca c nc trong 10 thng qua c t 616,24 t USD, tng 14,1%, tng ng tng 75,94 t USD v s tuyt i so vi cng k nm 2021. Trong , tng tr gi xut khu c t 312,82 t USD, tng 15,9% (tng ng tng 42,98 t USD) v tng tr gi nhp khu c t 303,42 t USD, tng 12,2% (tng ng tng 32,95 t USD). Nh vy, trong thng 10, c nc c xut siu 2,27 t USD. Tnh chung t u nm n ht thng 10-2022, c nc c tnh xut siu 9,4 t USD.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;Kt qu ny phn nh nhng c gng to ln ca Tng cc Hi quan, B Ti chnh v cc b, ngnh trong cng tc ci cch th tc hnh chnh v to thun li cho hot ng xut, nhp khu ca doanh nghip, Ph ch tch VCCI Hong Quang Phng nhn nh.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>a s doanh nghip hi lng vi th tc hi quan</strong></span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Nhn nh ca ng Hong Quang Phng c a ra trn c s kho st mc  hi lng ca doanh nghip v vic thc hin th tc hnh chnh qua C ch mt ca quc gia v cc th tc qun l, kim tra chuyn ngnh. Hot ng kho st ny c bt u t nm 2019. n nay, mi nm, VCCI u phi hp vi Tng cc Hi quan cng vi h tr t C quan Pht trin quc t Hoa K thng qua d n to thun li thng mi  kho st v cng b bo co.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Kt qu kho st ca hn 3.000 doanh nghip xut-nhp khu trong nm 2022 va c VCCI cng b cho thy, phn ln doanh nghip cho bit, Cng mt ca quc gia c vn hnh tng i tt; qu trnh thc hin th tc trc tuyn trn cng thun li hn; vic tip nhn v gii quyt th tc hnh chnh qua cng  gip gim thi gian, chi ph cho cc doanh nghip. Cc doanh nghip cng ghi nhn nhng chuyn bin tch cc tng t trong lnh vc qun l, kim tra chuyn ngnh.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ph v trng, Ph trng ban ph trch Ban Ci cch, hin i ha hi quan (Tng cc Hi quan) Lng Khnh Thit cho bit: \"Tnh n ngy 17-10-2022, Cng mt ca quc gia  c 250/261 th tc hnh chnh ca 13 b, ngnh kt ni, vi gn 5 triu b h s ca hn 55 nghn doanh nghip. Bn cnh vic trin khai C ch mt ca quc gia, C ch mt ca ASEAN, thi gian qua, ci cch, n gin ha th tc kim tra chuyn ngnh i vi hng ha xut-nhp khu c Chnh ph c bit quan tm, ch o quyt lit nhm to thun li cho doanh nghip, gim thi gian thng quan hng ha, ci thin Ch s giao dch thng mi qua bin gii, nng cao nng lc cnh tranh quc gia\".&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Cn nhiu vic phi lm</strong></span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Tuy vy, qua  kin ca cc doanh nghip cho thy, doanh nghip vn mong mun cc b, ngnh, c quan hu quan tip tc quan tm nng cao hiu qu ca Cng mt ca quc gia, ng thi y mnh ci cch th tc qun l, kim tra chuyn ngnh nhm to thun li thng mi nhiu hn na.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">V kim tra chuyn ngnh, cng ng doanh nghip nh gi, trnh t, th tc kim tra cn qua nhiu bc qu mc cn thit, khng thng nht; doanh nghip phi i li nhiu ln, tip xc vi nhiu u mi c quan nh nc; mt s th tc kim tra chuyn ngnh, qun l chuyn ngnh cn thc hin th cng; mt s th tc  chuyn sang hnh thc in t nhng cha ton din, mt s bc vn yu cu h s giy. Cc doanh nghip cng cho rng, s trng lp v kim tra chuyn ngnh gia cc b, ngnh cha c x l thng nht bng vic sa i, ban hnh vn bn quy phm php lut phn cng chc nng, nhim v; nhiu nhm hng cn chu s qun l ca nhiu b. c bit, doanh nghip phn nh cc b, ngnh vn cha p dng cng nhn ln nhau, tha nhn ln nhau; cha p dng truy xut ngun gc trong kim tra chuyn ngnh.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cc doanh nghip  ngh cc b, ngnh tip tc ct gim, n gin ha cc khu trong quy trnh kim tra chuyn ngnh, t np h s, kim tra h s, ly mu v thng bo kt qu; p dng y  v rng ri hn nguyn tc qun l ri ro  to iu kin tt hn cho cc doanh nghip c lch s tun th tt; gim n mc thp nht nhng im chng cho gia cc quy nh v kim tra chuyn ngnh.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cng vi , cng ng doanh nghip mong mun trin khai C ch mt ca quc gia nhanh hn v trit  hn  gim ti a cc giy t phi np, chuyn ti a sang s ha, trnh tnh trng doanh nghip va phi khai thng tin trn Cng mt ca quc gia, va phi lm th tc trc tip ti c quan qun l nh nc. Cc c quan nh nc cng cn c c ch kt ni, chia s thng tin  trnh yu cu trng lp vi cc doanh nghip.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> to thun li hn na cho doanh nghip, gim thi gian thng quan hng ha xut-nhp khu, Ph tng cc trng Tng cc Hi quan Hong Vit Cng khng nh, c quan hi quan s n lc phi hp vi cc b, ngnh, ng hnh vi doanh nghip  trin khai C ch mt ca quc gia, C ch mt ca ASEAN ng tin ; ci cch th tc kim tra chuyn ngnh  gim thi gian thng quan hng ha xut-nhp khu, to thun li cho doanh nghip, gp phn nng cao nng lc cnh tranh quc gia.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ngun: Bo Qun i Nhn dn Vit Nam&nbsp;</span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:15pt;margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify;\" dir=\"ltr\"><a style=\"text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.qdnd.vn/kinh-te/cac-van-de/bo-ganh-nang-voi-thu-tuc-hai-quan-710384\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#1155cc;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><u>https://www.qdnd.vn/kinh-te/cac-van-de/bo-ganh-nang-voi-thu-tuc-hai-quan-710384</u></span></i></span></a></p>'),(16,'Ln u tin t chc Trin lm Quc t chuyn ngnh Logistics','specialized_news','2023-06-02 08:20:47.148000','2023-08-10 16:59:15.735000','2023-06-02 08:22:05.388000',1,1,'vi-VN',1,'Logistics l mt trong nhng ngnh tng trng nhanh v n nh nht ca Vit Nam, vi tc  bnh qun t 14 - 16% mt nm, vi quy m 40 - 42 T /nm. Theo bng xp hng Agility 2022, Vit Nam c xp hng th 11 trong nhm 50 th trng logistics mi ni ton cu.','lan-dau-tien-to-chuc-trien-lam-quoc-te-chuyen-nganh-logistics',43,-1,0,'<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Logistics l mt trong nhng ngnh tng trng nhanh v n nh nht ca Vit Nam, vi tc  bnh qun t 14 - 16% mt nm, vi quy m 40 - 42 T /nm. Theo bng xp hng Agility 2022, Vit Nam c xp hng th 11 trong nhm 50 th trng logistics mi ni ton cu.</span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ln u tin ti Vit Nam, Trin lm quc t Logistics Vit Nam (tn vit tt VILOG) thuc s ch tr ca B Cng Thng Vit Nam (c th hai n v u mi l Cc y tin thng mi v Cc xut nhp khu) , c thc hin bi Hip hi Doanh nghip Dch v Logistics Vit Nam (VLA) v VINEXAD s chnh thc din ra trong 03 ngy, t ngy 10-12/8/2023 ti SECC (Nh B), 799 Nguyn Vn Linh, Qun 7 ,TPHCM.</span></span></p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:75%;\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\" src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/image_58c50d767b.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"401\" uploadprocessed=\"true\" alt=\"image.png\" srcset=\"https: