image_28702898fa.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"401\" uploadprocessed=\"true\" alt=\"image.png\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_image_28702898fa.png 234w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_image_28702898fa.png 500w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/medium_image_28702898fa.png 750w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/large_image_28702898fa.png 1000w\" sizes=\"100vw\"></figure><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#f3f4f5;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ln u tin ti Vit Nam, trin lm quc t chuyn ngnh Logistisc c t chc di s ch tr ca B Cng Thng Vit nam, Ch o bi Cc Xc tin thng mi, cng s phi hp cht ch vi Cc Xut nhp khu.</span></i></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Trin lm c t chc bi Hip hi Doanh nghip Dch v Logistics Vit Nam (VLA) v Nh t chc VINEXAD. S kt hp gia Hip hi mang \'ting ni c trng lng gia ngnh Logistics v mt nh t chc chuyn nghip vi kinh nghim v h thng mng li i tc su rng, k vng s to ra mt s kin gip thc y ngnh cng nghip Logistics Vit Nam pht trin tm nhn xa vi tim nng vn c, ng thi to ra ting vang ku gi thu ht u t nc ngoi, chuyn giao cng ngh vn hnh vn ti, o to nhn lc, thit lp h thng sinh thi xanh trong ngnh Logistics.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 15pt;\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.4;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding