></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.076923076923077;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 12pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Kinh t Vit Nam l mt nn kinh t m, da vo thng mi quc t khi c quan h kinh t song phng vi trn 230 nc v vng lnh th. Vit Nam cng  k kt 16 hip nh thng mi t do (FTA) vi 60 nn kinh t.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.076923076923077;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 12pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ngh quyt i hi ng ln th XIII  xc nh xy dng kt cu h tng ng b l 1 trong 3 t ph chin lc  pht trin t nc. Thc hin nhim v trn, chng ta  tng bc nng cp ng b, ng st, ng khng, ng bin, ng thy ni a gia cc a phng v kt ni ng thi vi cc nc.</span></span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:2.076923076923077;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 12pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:Arial;font-size:11.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Tuy nhin, vic ng dng cng ngh s trong doanh nghip logistics ni ring v trong cc doanh nghip Vit Nam ni chung cn nhiu hn ch v ang i mt vi khong cch ln v Tr tu nhn to (AI). Theo s liu thng k, u t vo cc cng ty gii php AI th Vit Nam v Philippines u di mc 1 USD trn u ngi trong khi Singapore vi 68 USD, Trung Quc 21 USD v Hoa K t 155 USD. iu  i hi Vit Nam cn phi u t mnh m hn na  tn dng nn tng k thut s trong sn xut v phn phi hng ha, thc y tng trng kinh t ca t 