coration:none;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ViettlLogisticsTuyenDung\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#1155cc;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><u>https://www.facebook.com/ViettlLogisticsTuyenDung</u></span></span></a></li></ul>'),(43,'VIETTEL POST EXPRESS DELIVERY OF GOODS AUSTRALIA - VIETNAM','internal_news','2023-06-05 02:18:23.366000','2023-08-10 07:44:35.200000','2023-06-05 02:18:26.454000',1,1,'en',1,'Realizing the market potential as well as the strength in the field of Logistics, in June 2023, Viettel Post joined the Australia-Vietnam express delivery network with services including: Delivery of e-commerce goods on behalf of customers. client; Shipping goods from Australia to Vietnam for individual and corporate customers; Services of customs clearance, import.','viettel-post-express-delivery-of-goods-australia-vietnam',211,16,11,'<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><strong>Potential from Vietnam\'s 7th largest trading partner</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">This information was given at the 4th meeting of the Working Group on Trade under the framework of the Vietnam - Australia Economic Partnership Ministerial Conference held at the end of March 2023. Accordingly, in 2022, two-way trade results between Vietnam and Australia have grown impressively, bilateral turnover in 2022 will reach 15.7 billion USD (Source: Website of the Ministry of Industry and Trade).</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Along with that, in response to the 50th anniversary of diplomatic relations between Vietnam and Australia, in order to further promote bilateral trade relations, commensurate with the strategic partnership, and at the same time bring trade relations in a balanced direction. In a fair and sustainable manner, Vietnam and Australia agreed to promote the implementation of a number of important cooperation contents, including cooperation and experience sharing in trade promotion and supply chain (Logistics).</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">According to Statista (Global Digital Economy Data Portal), currently, Australia is in the TOP 10 countries with the largest global parcel delivery (CEP) revenue with about 12.2 billion USD and is expected to grow at a compound annual rate (CARG) of 5.46% in the period 2022-2027.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">In Vietnam, CEP revenue is estimated to reach USD 0.71 billion in 2021 and is expected to reach USD 4.48 billion in 2030 with a CARG of 24.1%. The volume of CEP goods from Australia to Vietnam is estimated at an average of 200 tons/month to Noi Bai and Tan Son Nhat airports.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Besides, with about 335,000 Vietnamese people living, studying and working in Australia, Australia-Vietnam trade and logistics activities are considered to be a promising market.</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><strong>Viettel Post joins Australia-Vietnam express delivery network</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Realizing the market potential as well as the strength in the field of Logistics, in June 2023, Viettel Post joined the Australia-Vietnam express delivery network with services including: Delivery of e-commerce goods on behalf of customers. client; Shipping goods from Australia to Vietnam for individual and corporate customers; Services of customs clearance, import.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">With a network of post offices in 63 provinces and cities across the country, Viettel Post\'s Australian - Vietnamese express delivery service makes a difference when providing fast home delivery (D2D) without going through a third party. father. This helps shorten the shipping process when the goods arrive at the customer\'s hands only take from 5 working days.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">As of June 2023, Viettel Post is one of the leading delivery companies in Vietnam, owns a network of more than 4,000 delivery points nationwide, nearly 40,000 professional employees, 2,000 trucks type of operation 24/24; with a successful delivery rate always reaching 95%.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"width:66.81%;\" src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/vtp_c40559ea71.jpg\" alt=\"vtp.jpg\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_vtp_c40559ea71.jpg 245w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_vtp_c40559ea71.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"500\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><i>With a nationwide network of post offices, Viettel Post ensures smooth transportation to all parts of the country</i></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Taking advantage of the available potential in the postal sector helps Viettel Post to optimize operating costs. This helps customers to use the service at the best cost. For regular customers, Viettel Post has more favorable discounts for customers.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">The presence in Australia helps and provides delivery services to help Viettel Post support and meet the needs of customers quickly and synchronously right from the time of receiving the goods.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Before joining the Australia-Vietnam express delivery route, Viettel Post was the first postal enterprise doing business in foreign markets and successfully connected 23/23 provinces of Cambodia. After Cambodia, Viettel Post continues to develop services in Myanmar and connects with more than 200 countries around the world. In the long-term strategy, the entry of Viettel Post in the Australian market will serve as a basis for Viettel Post to continue to expand return routes from China, Japan, Korea, the US and European countries...</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Customers in Australia who want to ship goods to Vietnam can send goods at Viettel Post pick-up point:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Address: Lot.06, 14-16 Belmore Road, Punchbowl NSW 2196.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Hotline in Australia: (+61) 406448688</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Hotline in Vietnam: (+84) 19008095 ext 2</span></p>'),(44,'VIETTEL POST IS THE ONLY LOGISTICS UNIT IN THE WORLD WIN IT WORLD AWARDS 2023 GOLD AWARD','internal_news','2023-06-05 02:18:41.790000','2023-08-07 05:21:25.200000','2023-06-05 02:18:42.886000',1,1,'en',NULL,'According to the announcement of the Organizing Committee of the world\'s largest information technology award - IT World Awards 2023, Viettel Post has won 3 consecutive gold awards for the NOC (Network Operation Center) system.','viettel-post-is-the-only-logistics-uniy-in-the-world-win-it-world-awards',38,2,1,'<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><b style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:bolder;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><i style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\"><strong>According to the announcement of the Organizing Committee of the world\'s largest information technology award - IT World Awards 2023, Viettel Post has won 3 consecutive gold awards for the NOC (Network Operation Center) system.</strong></i></b></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">This is one of the most prestigious technology awards in the world, attracting the participation of many large enterprises and corporations in Vietnam and internationally. The award is also an annual activity for businesses and corporations to affirm the quality of digital technology products and services to foreign partners.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">This year, Viettel Post\'s NOC system won 3 gold awards in the following categories: IT Solutions for Technology, Most Innovative IT Service, and Transportation Management Systems. transportation management system).</span></p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:59.69%;\"><img src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/z4468202106913_0fcffe7a7f5a706a5692861b4f64c2db_2615c8e86b.jpg\" alt=\"z4468202106913_0fcffe7a7f5a706a5692861b4f64c2db.jpg\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_z4468202106913_0fcffe7a7f5a706a5692861b4f64c2db_2615c8e86b.jpg 234w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_z4468202106913_0fcffe7a7f5a706a5692861b4f64c2db_2615c8e86b.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"500\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><em style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:center;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><i>The NOC system is also known as the \"magic eye\" of Viettel Post</i></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">In particular, Viettel Post won the absolute victory when up to 3 out of 3 nomination categories all won the Gold award for the NOC system. This result is evaluated and approved by leading experts in the field of Information Technology from all over the world. This is also the third year in a row that Viettel Post has won at the IT World Awards.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Notably, in the field of Logistics, Viettel Post is the only enterprise in Vietnam and in the world to be honored at the IT World Awards 2023.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">To be recognized at this nomination, Viettel Post\'s NOC system has proven to be effective in practice and is exploited and used regularly. Specifically, after 8 months of implementation, NOC has monitored 372 quality indicators, 241 business indicators of 63 branches, 72 exploitation centers in the province, and nearly 11,088 postmen nationwide.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">The NOC system helps Viettel Post\'s operations department reduce the reporting time per day through 360-degree data cutting. The daily report aggregation of postal staff is reduced to 15-30 minutes instead of 1-2 hours as before. Retrieving data only takes 1-2 minutes compared to 20-30 minutes like when processing manually due to having to aggregate many different data sources.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Information is extracted multi-dimensionally and brought numbers to life by connecting data belonging to different modules from business, finance to customer service... Thanks to that, users have an overall picture. and operational logic to get an overview to help make quick, accurate decisions.</span></p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:68.34%;\"><img src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/z4468203905736_fe1e9f72fd88d3469699699710520675_73bb251f3e.jpg\" alt=\"z4468203905736_fe1e9f72fd88d3469699699710520675.jpg\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_z4468203905736_fe1e9f72fd88d3469699699710520675_73bb251f3e.jpg 245w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_z4468203905736_fe1e9f72fd88d3469699699710520675_73bb251f3e.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"500\"></figure><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">In addition, Viettel Post\'s NOC system helps management levels to identify \"weaknesses\" in each service stage to make timely decisions to shorten operation time, improve service quality and prevent prevent unexpected incidents. The warning of arising problems is updated in real time, so errors will be detected and handled immediately.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Before the NOC system, every day, Viettel Post\'s operation department needed to work continuously with raw data sources in large quantities, which caused inadequacies in terms of time and accuracy of data. number. Therefore, the NOC system was \"born out of pain\" to help operate and centrally monitor all functional modules at Viettel Post from business, operations, finance, labor organization to customer care. row</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">As planned in 2023, the NOC system will continue to perfect, add new modules and functions, put into operation the automatic task assignment flow according to vouchers applied to units, fully upgrade improve the system. The NOC system monitors and operates 100% of the indicators in real time to help alert, operate accurately, quickly and improve customer experience. At the same time, the system development team of Viettel Post will also add an interface on the App to make the NOC system easy to use in monitoring and operating.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">The recognition of the world\'s largest information technology award - IT World Awards 2023 is a milestone in Viettel Post\'s argument shifting process. Determining that service quality is the most important driving force for growth, Viettel Post always researches and applies technology in operation, monitoring and warning to each order, each postal route, and each vehicle. This is also Viettel Post\'s commitment to provide the most optimal shipping solution for customers with the motto \"Fastest - Most reliable\".</span></p><div class=\"main-content\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><div class=\"section-listpost\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-left:auto;margin-right:a