><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Th tc gi bu gi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> M bu gi  giao dch vin kim tra ni dung, chng t i km</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Gi bc bu gi theo quy nh ca Bu chnh Viettel (VTP), cn, nim phong, i chiu cc ph vi bng gi v gi km y  ha n, chng t.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> in y  thng tin, k, ghi r h tn vo mt trc v mt sau phiu gi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Lu lin 3 phiu gi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Quyn ca Ngi gi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> c Viettel Post cung cp y  thng tin lin quan n toan b quy trinh cung ng Dich vu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> c Viettel Post m bo b mt thng tin, an ton i vi Bu gi trong toan qu trnh giao hng theo qui nh ca php lut.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> c Viettel Post gii quyt khiu ni, c giai quyt thoa ang v Dch v cung ng  s dng.  c Viettel Post bi thng thit hi tuy theo thc t tng trng hp.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Ngha v ca Ngi gi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Thc hin vic i soat cc phi Dch v am bao ung thi han.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Khng gi Bu gi cha c lu thng trn th trng, hng cm, hng hn ch vn chuyn/kinh doanh hoc hng kinh doanh c iu kin nhng khng cung cp c giy php.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Khch hng c ngha v m hng v phi hp vi Viettel Post trong vic ng kim cng nh nim phong hng ha khi gi hng.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Chu trch nhim trc Viettel Post v trc php lut v ni dung Bu gi, ha n, chng t ngun gc xut x cua Bu gi v chng t nh km.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Chu trch nhim lm vic, gii quyt vi C quan c thm quyn khi Bu gi tm gi hoc tch thu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Cung cp y  ha n, chng t ca Bu gi cho Viettel Post khi gi Bu gi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Viettel Post s c min tr trch nhim bi thng trong trng hp Bu gi b tm gi hoc tch thu bi c quan c thm quyn do Bu gi khng c ha n, chng t hp php nh km.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> ng gi Bu gi theo ng tng quy cch, kch thc v tnh cht ca tng mt hng, c bit i vi Bu gi l cc mt hng d v.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Cung cp y u ch dn lin quan n Bu gi; thng tin lin quan n Ngi gi, Ngi nhn trn Bu gi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Bi thng thit hi thc t cho Viettel Post v bn th 3 c lin quan khi thit hi xy ra co ngun gc t Khch hng/Ngi gi theo quy nh ca php lut.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Chu trch nhim v mi thng tin lin quan n Ngi nhn m Khch hng giao cho Viettel Post. Trng hp xy ra sai st v thng tin Ngi nhn hoc Bu gi khng ng yu cu ca Ngi nhn th Khch hng c trch nhim t gii quyt vi Ngi nhn, ng thi Khch hng vn phi thanh ton Cc ph Dch v i vi n hng trn da trn l trnh  thc hin.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Bng chi ph ca mnh, chu trch nhim gii quyt cc vn  lin quan n tranh chp v quyn s hu Bu gi, ngun gc Bu gi vi bn th ba bt k; hoc khiu ni ca Ngi nhn v vic hng ha b li, khng ng yu cu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tip nhn v gii quyt khiu ni Thi hiu khiu ni</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Bu gi suy suyn, h hng, gi cc, ni dung khc: 01 thng k t ngy bu gi pht thnh cng.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Mt mt, chuyn pht bu gi chm: 06 thng k t ngy kt thc thi gian ton trnh.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Thi gian gii quyt khiu ni khng qu 02 thng i vi bu gi trong nc; khng qu 03 thng i vi bu gi quc t.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> VTP tip nhn, x l khiu ni bng: cng vn, tng i 19008095, hoc giao dch vin trc tip.</p>'),(57,'PAYMENT POLICIES','internal_news','2023-06-30 08:16:07.561000','2023-08-14 01:31:12.418000','2023-06-30 08:19:51.759000',1,1,'en',NULL,'Voso.vn is an e-commerce transaction floor (referred to as Voso.vn) that allows organizations and individuals to buy and sell goods online. Voso.vn is built to provide domestic and international goods buying and selling application, linking with other e-commerce floors to offer many options for buyers.\n\nObjective: To become the number