am, tin nc ngoi v cc giy t c gi tr nh tin.<br>- Cc loi kim kh qu (vng, bc, bch kim), cc loi  qu hay cc sn phm khc c ch bin t kim kh qu,  qu.<br>Lu : Viettel Logistics khng chu trch nhim v vic h hng, tht lc hng ha hay b Php lut truy cu nu bn c  gi cc hng ha b cm trn.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>2. Ti c th thanh ton n hng bng cc hnh thc no?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt; Bn c th thanh ton n hng theo nhng cch sau:</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">- Thanh ton cho nhn vin giao hng<br>- Trc tip ti vn phng ca Viettel Logistics</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>3. Hng ha ca ti c c m bo cht lng khi giao?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt; Tt c hng ha u m bo  an ton v cht lng. Viettel Logistics tun th ng cc yu cu v bo qun hng ha trong qu trnh vn chuyn v cam kt giao ng v  hng ha n tn tay khch hng.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>4. Bo him gi tr hng ha l g?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt;100% hng ha ca Viettel Logistics u c m bo gi tr hng ha. y l chnh sch n b cho khch hng trong trng hp hng ha b h hng, tht lc trong qu trnh vn chuyn.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>5. Gi hng ha c cn iu kin, chng t g km theo khng?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt;  m bao giao ng ngi nhn, nhanh chng v an ton, bn cn in v dn phiu gi ln kin hng hoc vit m vn n ln kin hng. Ngoi ra, bn khng cn cung cp chng t i km nu hng ha khng nm trong danh mc hng gi c iu kin c quy nh nh sau:</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">- Bu phm, bu kin cha hng ha  kinh doanh phi c chng t thu v cc chng t hp l khc theo quy nh ca php lut.<br>- Vt phm, hng ha xut khu, nhp khu thuc qun l chuyn ngnh phi thc hin theo quy nh ca c quan qun l chuyn ngnh c thm quyn.<br>- Ong, tm, a, cn trng phc v nghin cu khoa hc, vt phm, hng ha d h hng, cht bt ng gi phi m bo  khng h hng,  nhim bu phm, bu kin khc.<br>- Vt phm, hng ha gi trong bu phm, bu kin s dng dch v my bay phi tun theo nhng quy nh v an ninh hng khng.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lu : Bn vui lng tun theo v thc hin ng v  cc iu kin rng buc i vi loi hng ha trn. Trong trng hp c tnh gi hng khng tun theo quy nh, Viettel Logistics s khng chu trch nhim nu xy ra h hng, tht lc hoc b php lut truy cu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>6. Ti c th gi hng  u? Viettel Logistics c nhn hng ti nh khng?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt; Hin nay, Viettel Logistics c mng li cc bu cc, chi nhnh ph khp 63/63 tnh thnh. Bn c th n bu cc gn nht hoc yu cu Viettel Logistics n nhn hng ti nh. Danh sch cc bu cc vui lng xem ti y.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>7. Ti cn lm g khi khiu ni v hng ha</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt; Bn c th kim tra tnh trng hng ha ngay khi nhn c hng (nu c bn gi ng ). Sau khi nhn hng nu pht hin hng ha b h hng vui lng lin h vi bu t hoc nhn tin cho chng ti  c h tr nhanh nht.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"> Thi hiu khiu ni: L thi hn khch hng c quyn khiu ni theo quy nh ca php lut (iu 38. Khiu ni trong cung ng v s dng dch v bu chnh<br> Lut bu chnh s 49/2010/QH12 ngy 17/06/2010). Thi hiu khiu ni c quy nh nh sau:<br>+ 06 thng, k t ngy kt thc thi gian ton trnh ca bu gi i vi khiu ni v vic mt bu gi, chuyn pht bu gi chm so vi thi gian ton trnh  cng b.<br>+ 01 thng, k t ngy bu gi c pht cho ngi nhn i vi khiu ni v vic bu gi b suy suyn, h hng, v gi cc v cc ni dung khc c lin quan trc tip n bu gi.<br>- Thi hn gii quyt khiu ni: (iu 38. Khiu ni trong cung ng v s dng dch v bu chnh  Lut bu chnh s 49/2010/QH12 ngy 17/06/2010).<br>+ Khng qu 02 thng, k t ngy nhn c khiu ni i vi dch v bu chnh trong nc.<br>+ Khng qu 03 thng, k t ngy nhn c khiu ni i vi dch v bu chnh quc t.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i><strong>8. Gi tr bi hon hng ha c tnh nh th no?</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">=&gt; Viettel Logistics thc hin bi hon hng ha theo 1 trong 3 trng hp sau:</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">- Khch hng  mua dch v bo him hng ha: bi hon 100% gi tr thit hi. Ti a 100 triu/ bu gi (gi tr hng ha ln hn 100 triu, khch hng t mua bo him hng ha ca cc Cng ty bo him).<br>- Khch hng s dng dch v thu tin COD: bi hon ti a 100% s tin thu h khng bao gm li nhun v khng qu 30 triu ng. (Ghi ch: n v gc c bin bn tha thun bi thng gim gi ti a da theo gi tr u vo ca bu gi).<br>- Khch hng khng s dng dch v bo him hng ha: Ga tr bi hon da vo hp ng do hai bn k kt.<br>+ Nu khch hng cung cp c chng t chng minh gi tr thit hi, bi hon 50% gi tr thit hi nhng khng qu 30 triu ng/1 bu gi.<br>+ Nu khch hng khng cung cp c chng t chng minh thit hi dch v bu chnh trong nc bi thng 4 ln cc ( bao gm hon tr li cc dch v  s dng) ca dch v  s dng.<br>+ Khng qu 02 thng, k t ngy nhn c khiu ni i vi dch v bu chnh trong nc.<br>+ Khng qu 03 thng, k t ngy nhn c khiu ni i vi dch v bu chnh quc t.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Ch : Chng t chng minh gi tr thit hi c th l ha n ti chnh, chng t chuyn khon c xc nhn ca ngn hng hoc hp ng mua bn.</p>'),(59,'SHIPPING POLICY','internal_news','2023-07-05 06:47:17.934000','2023-08-14 08:44:40.837000','2023-07-05 06:48:05.844000',1,1,'en',NULL,'1. Does Viettel Logistics accept large and bulky goods?','SHIPPING POLICY',18,0,0,'<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>1. Does Viettel Logistics accept large and bulky goods?</strong><br>=&gt; Viettel Logistics receives and transports all kinds of goods in accordance with the provisions of the Law. Types of goods prohibited from sending (according to State regulations) include:<br>- Narcotics and psychostimulants<br>- Weapons, ammunition, military-technical equipment, artifacts belonging to historical and cultural relics.<br>- All kinds of depraved, reactionary cultural products, publications, and documents aimed at destroying public order against the State of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam.<br>- Explosive, flammable objects or substances and substances that are dangerous or unsanitary, causing environmental pollution.<br>-Types of articles and goods that the State prohibits from circulation, business, or import and export.<br>- Articles, publications, and goods are banned from entering the receiving country according to the notice of the Universal Postal Union (UPU).<br>-Letters in parcels (letters enclosed in goods).<br>- Articles and goods in letters, publications, and school supplies for the blind (Decree 142/2004/ND-CP dated July 8, 2014).<br>- Postal items contain many items, sent to many different receiving addresses.<br>- Living creature.<br>- Vietnamese currency, foreign currency, and valuable papers such as money.<br>- Precious metals (gold, silver, platinum...), precious stones, or other products made from precious metals and gems.<br>Viettel Logistics is not responsible for the damage, loss of goods, or being prosecuted by the Law if you intentionally send the above-prohibited goods.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>2. How can I pay for my order?</strong><br>=&gt; You can pay for your order in the following ways:<br>- Payment for delivery staff<br>- Directly at the office of Viettel Logistics</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>3. Is my goods guaranteed for delivery?</strong><br>=&gt; All goods are guaranteed for safety and quality. Viettel Logistics strictly complies with the requirements of goods preservation during transportation and commits to deliver the right and sufficient goods to customers.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>4. What is Cargo Value Insurance?</strong><br>=&gt; 100% of Viettel Logistics goods are guaranteed value of goods. This is the olicy to compensate customers in case the goods are damaged or lost during transportation.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>5. Is there any conditions or documents required to send the goods?</strong><br>&gt; To ensure delivery to the right recipient, quickly and safely, you need to print and stick the consignment note on the package or write the waybill code on the package. In addition, you do not need to provide supporting documents if the goods are not on the list of conditional consignments specified as follows:<br>- Postal items and parcels containing goods for business must have tax vouchers and other valid documents as prescribed by law.<br>-Export and import articles and goods under specialized management must comply with regulations of competent specialized management agencies.<br>- Bees, silkworms, leeches, insects in service of scientific research, perishable articles and goods, and packaged powder must ensure that they do not damage or contaminate other mailers and parcels.<br>-Articles and goods sent in postal items and parcels using aircraft services must comply with aviation security regulations.<br>Lu : Please follow and perform properly and fully the binding conditions for the above goods. In case of deliberately sending goods that do not comply with regulations, Viettel Logistics will not be responsible if damaged, lost or prosecuted by law.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>6. Where can I ship items? Does Viettel Logistics receive goods at home?</strong><br>=&gt; Currently, Viettel Logistics has a network of post offices and branches covering 63/63 provinces in Viet Nam. You can go to the nearest post office or ask Viettel Logistics to pick up the goods at home. List of post offices, please click here.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>7. What do I need to do when I want to make a complaint about goods?</strong><br>&gt; You can check the condition of the goods as soon as you receive them (if agreed by the sender). After receiving the goods, if you find that the goods are damaged, please contact the post office or message us for the fastest support.<br> Statute of limitations for complaints: The time limit for customers to make complaints according to the provisions of the law (Article 38. Complaints in the provision and use of postal services  Postal Law No. 49/2010/QH12 dated 17/02) June 2010). The statute of limitations for complaints is specified as follows:<br>+ 06 months from the end of the postal processing time, for complaints about the loss of postal items or delayed delivery of the items compared to the announced transit time.<br>+ 01 month from the date the postal item is delivered to the recipient, for complaints about the item being lost or damaged, about the freight rate and other contents directly related to the item.<br>- Time limit for settlement of complaints: (Article 38. Complaints in the provision and use of postal services  Postal Law No. 49/2010/QH12 dated June 17, 2010).<br>+ No more than 02 months from the date of receipt of complaints about domestic postal services.<br>+ No more than 03 months from the date of receipt of complaints about international postal services.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><br><strong>8. How is the return value of goods calculated?</strong><br>&gt; Viettel Logistics will refund goods in one of the following three cases:<br> Customers who have purchased cargo insurance services: 100% refund of damage value. Maximum 100 million/ postal item (the value of goods is greater than 100 million, customers buy insurance by themselves from insurance companies).<br>- Customers using COD collection service: refund up to 100% of the collected amount excluding profits and not more than 30 million VND. (Note: the original unit has a written agreement to compensate for the maximum discount based on the input value of the postal item).<br>- Customers who do not use cargo insurance services: The reimbursement value is based on the contract signed by both parties.<br>+ If the customer provides documents proving the damage value, refund 50% of the damage value but not more than VND 30 million / 1 postal item.<br>+ If the customer fails to provide proof of damage to the domestic postal service, compensate 4 times the freight (including refund of used service charges) of the used service.<br>Documents proving the damage value can be financial invoices, bank transfer documents or sales contracts.<br>&nbsp;</p>');
